name: Introducing... Bun-Bun: Down the Rabbit Hole
description: Remember our tender friend Observation Cranium? Let’s check in and see how he is doing. He is deeply rooted and doesn’t really travel but he can still make friends! Looks like he has made a new one now! Bun-Bun the friendly fluffy bunny. No one knows where she came from, or how she grew that tree she hopped out from under so fast, but she seems nice enough. She has invited us to follow her home! Shall we go? Down the Rabbit Hole? 2048x2048px Digital Drawing by Katie Kraft @artistAKAKatie.com
